                        <interp inst="t18480703-name-264" type="given" value="JOHNS"></interp>JOHNS WHITEHEAD</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Dock-street, Whitechapel—it is my dwelling-house. Mortimer is my grandson—he came to me about 9th June—next morning I found my chest broken open, and all the articles gone—the things are here—they are mine.</p>
